{"type": "article", "id": 6240, "title": "Panst's Gift 潘斯特的礼物", "description": null, "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": null, "column": null, "author": 3603, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/default_images/missing_article.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;padding:0px;color:#737373;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"color:#737373;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604213940oQzLqvZkw70txKUu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;padding:0px;color:#737373;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"color:#737373;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;\">听说过潘斯特星球吗？你即使没听说过，但如果你看到这个长着长耳朵的外星人的形象，就一定会觉得面熟。潘斯特是由国内一个叫崇子的女孩设计的简单可爱的卡通外星人。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;padding:0px;color:#737373;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"color:#000000;\">而潘斯特的礼物就是该团队</span><a href=\"http://114.112.40.205/?p=670\" style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;color:#0069D6;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">与瑞众联创合作推出的一款卡牌游戏</span></a><span style=\"color:#000000;\">，该游戏规则简单易上手，而且关键在于萌！萌！萌！老同学相见还是玩这种温暖可爱风格的卡牌为好，如果拿出来的是 Cards Against Humanity 这套卡牌的话，估计没两局人就跑光了。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;padding:0px;color:#737373;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"color:#000000;\">价格 29 元左右，购买可以戳</span><a href=\"http://s.taobao.com/search?q=%C5%CB%CB%B9%CC%D8%B5%C4%C0%F1%CE%EF&amp;js=1&amp;stats_click=search_radio_all%253A1&amp;initiative_id=staobaoz_20150210\" style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;color:#0069D6;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">这里</span></a><span style=\"color:#000000;\">。</span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}